[I] Run arbitrary commands when files change

[T] A utility for running arbitrary commands when files change. Uses kqueue(2)
[T] or inotify(7) to avoid polling entr was written to facilitate rapid
[T] feedback on the command line.

[U] https://eradman.com/entrproject

[A] Eric Radman <ericshane@eradman.com>
[M] T2 Project <t2@t2-project.org>

